 understandable.<br><br>Verant should allow one day of training so we can all go back and find that one idiot who trained you over and over. &quot;Ding&quot; had the perfect cartoon for it (something about revenge being served 20 levels later), but I don't have the webpage bookmarked. <br>Oh well, I'm pretty sure the next 10 posts will be telling me how wrong I am for understanding why he did what he did anyhow. =) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f7f7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/uberlysometa.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Berly Someta</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Scowling Poster</span><br> <font color=#778899>(1/30/02 2:48:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/finnoruukserverfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=388.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re:</span><hr size=1> bah This was supposed to be posted as a repy to &quot;In Sight out of mind!&quot;...guess I hit the wrong button. =) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f7f7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/binnoruukserver.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=samira>Samira</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Indifferent Poster</span><br> <font color=#778899>(1/30/02 3:01:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/finnoruukserverfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=388.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Re:</span><hr size=1> I think everyone understands. I understand. I also understand why people beat, rob and kill each other. Doesn't mean I condone it or offer moral support to others when they do it.<br><br> <p><img src=http://iseult.sidhe.freewebspace.com/images/samira.jpg></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f7f7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboar